查看之前未发布的 Aphex Twin 曲目“th1 [evnslower]” https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-previously-unreleased-aphex-twin-track-th1-evnslower-3790944?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=check-out-previously-unreleased-aphex-双轨-th1-evnslowerAnagricel Duran Thu, 05 Sep 2024 14:10:19 +0000 Music NewsNewsElectronic https://www.nme.com/?p=3790944 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="APHEX TWIN 的照片（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这首歌是继他的扩展版“Selected Ambient Works II”中的“#19”之后分享的第二首歌曲</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/check-out-previously-unreleased-aphex-twin-track-th1-evnslower-3790944">查看之前未发行的 Aphex Twin 曲目“th1 [evnslower]”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="APHEX TWIN 的照片（摄影：Mick Hutson/Redferns）" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/Aphex-Twin-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/Aphex-Twin">Aphex Twin</a>之前未发行的歌曲“th1 [evnslower]”现在首次在所有流媒体平台上提供。 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：</strong><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/aphex-twin-at-printworks-2549628-2549628"><b>伦敦 Printworks 的 Aphex Twin：仍然是地球上最伟大的电子展之一</b></a></li></ul><p>由 Warp Records 分享的《th1 [evnslower]》是 Aphex Twin <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/aphex-twin-announces-30th-anniversary-box-set-of-classic-selected-ambient-works-volume-ii-3766729">扩展版《Selected Ambient Works II》</a>中分享的第二首歌曲，该版本将于 10 月 4 日发行。您可以<a href="https://aphextwin.warp.net/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处预订</a>。</p><p>这首 11 分钟的精简歌曲具有令人难忘和怪异的音景，让人想起星际恐怖电影。它遵循之前发布的曲目“#19”，该曲目之前被称为“Stone In Focus”，并且仅提供黑胶唱片。 </p><p><iframe title="Aphex Twin - th1 [evnslower]（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CoM0JarMMvo?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> 1994 年发行的《Selected Ambient Works Volume II》是他的首张 LP《Selected Ambient Works 85–92》的后续作品，与 Aphex Twin 之前的作品不同，其声音主要是无节拍的。这张专辑发行后，在英国专辑排行榜上名列第 11 位，被认为是这位电子音乐家从环境科技音乐到黑暗环境音乐的广受好评的转变。</p><p> Aphex Twin 专辑的重新发行将包含折叠式海报、贴纸和小册子，其中包含保罗·尼克尔森 (Paul Nicholson) 的艺术创作草图。它将采用铰链橡木盒和蚀刻铜板。每份副本都是独一无二的，并且都是按订单制作的。它将以 4-LP 套装、3-CD 套装和豪华 4-LP 盒装形式提供。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C8W6B3sonO0/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; 